## New Capabilities Delivered

### 1. Interactive TUI (`prb tui`)
- Query language with boolean logic + field filtering
- 4 panes: Event List, Decode Tree, Hex Dump, Timeline
- Live mode with ring buffer

### 2. Export Formats (`prb export`)
- CSV, HTML, HAR, OTLP exporters

### 3. Live Capture (`prb capture`)
- Real-time packet capture with filters
- Integration with MCAP storage + TUI

### 4. Parallel Pipeline (`prb --jobs`)
- Rayon-based parallel normalization
- Flow-partitioned TCP reassembly
- Streaming pipeline with backpressure

### 5. Protocol Detection
- 5 built-in detectors (HTTP/2, gRPC, ZMTP, RTPS, TLS)
- Native + WASM plugin systems
- Plugin CLI: list, info, install, remove

### 6. OTel Trace Correlation
- 4 propagation formats (W3C, B3, Jaeger, Datadog)
- CLI filtering by trace ID

